#. Tag: para
#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: index.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Opens a dialog which allows you to create a puzzle from an image on your disk.</action> See <link linkend=\"create-puzzles\">the corresponding section</link> for details and also <link linkend=\"large-puzzle-creation\">special concerns</link>, if you are going to create a puzzle with 300 or more pieces."
